484
00:39:19.920 --> 00:39:21.960
Adik Qingyun, ayo, naik kereta kuda.

485
00:39:22.440 --> 00:39:22.960
Baik.

486
00:39:35.830 --> 00:39:37.000
Ning Yuxuan, asal tahu saja,

487
